OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some sunshine,
OL,7,Fespecially for Shetland and western
OL,8,FOrkney, with areas of cloud around
OL,9,FFair Isles and east Orkney. Patchy
OL,10,Fhaar developing tonight, and a general
OL,11,Fincrease in cloud.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA dry day with some low
OL,14,Fcloud and perhaps a few coastal fog
OL,15,Fpatches, but the chance of some sunny
OL,16,Fintervals here and there, the best
OL,17,Fchance for eastern Shetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
