OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA mainly
OL,6,Fdry few days with some bright spells,
OL,7,Falthough a fair amount of cloud around
OL,8,Fat times. Best chance of sunshine will
OL,9,Fbe on Saturday.
